Company Overview of Partnership Capital Growth, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Partnership Capital Growth, LLC is a private equity and venture capital firm specializing in investments in growth capital, mezzanine financing, bridge financing, PIPEs, private placements, buyouts, mid venture, and late venture in middle market companies. It typically invests in consumer products, technology, and services focused on healthy, active, and sustainable living market companies including supplements and natural organic products, controlled weight management, and wellness information and technology. The firm invests in companies having revenue at or approaching at least $10 million and enterprise values between $50 million to the $500 million and a positive EBIDTA history. Partner...
Partnership Capital Growth, LLC is a private equity and venture capital firm specializing in investments in growth capital, mezzanine financing, bridge financing, PIPEs, private placements, buyouts, mid venture, and late venture in middle market companies. It typically invests in consumer products, technology, and services focused on healthy, active, and sustainable living market companies including supplements and natural organic products, controlled weight management, and wellness information and technology. The firm invests in companies having revenue at or approaching at least $10 million and enterprise values between $50 million to the $500 million and a positive EBIDTA history. Partnership Capital Growth, LLC is based in San Francisco, California with additional offices at Boston, Massachusetts and Chicago, Illinois.
Detailed Description


