Capital Growth Solutions – The Gold Standard for SBA Lender Service Providers. 
Capital Growth Solutions, LLC began operations in May of 2008 to fill a void in the SBA commercial lending market. Small and mid-sized bank and community lenders wished to participate in U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA) financing programs, yet lacked the expertise to do so. Over the last several years, we’ve helped dozens of organizations turn this underutilized service into a highly profitable portion of their business, and we know that we can do the same for your institution.

 Questions? We can help.Get In Touch With CAPGS  











Gary Griffin, President & CEO, on why Capital Growth Solutions is the perfect “outsourced” SBA loan department.

 











 
Gary Griffin – Why CGS? from Capital Growth Solutions on Vimeo.












What Some Our Clients Are Saying










We have been clients with Capital Growth Solutions for 3 years at this bank. I previously worked with Gary for about 10 years with another bank. All dealings have been as agreed. Gary has a very good relationship with SBA and is able to satisfy their requirements in a timely manner. We have closed over $10MM and will continue to use them for our SBA lending.		


David K. Craig 
- CEO
American Trust Bank of East Tennessee








