Ronald J. Wallace 
- Former EVP/Commercial Lending LOB Manager








We have been contracted with CGS since March 2011. Since then, we have enjoyed a great relationship. They worked hard getting our then existing SBA portfolio in good condition. They have serviced our portfolio with SBA and Colson to all of our expectations. When we had issues with the servicing end of the business, CGS was attentive to resolving those issues to the satisfaction of all concerned. During the 2 ½ years we have been with them, they assisted us in liquidating two 7A loans. These were loans created before we contracted with CGS and we were concerned about the outcome. However, CGS packaged and presented the guaranty request and we received the full claim. CGS is a valuable partner that continues to be very responsive and easily accessible to our ongoing SBA needs. We are very satisfied with the service, knowledge and partnership we have with Gary and his staff.		


